\r\n			<p>Our mission is to make the world safer, healthier, and smarter through innovative technology. We envision a world where your home seamlessly responds to your needs, offering full control and security no matter where you are.</p>		\r\n			<h2>Product and Services</h2>		\r\n		<p><strong>Smart of Things</strong> brings the future of home automation and security into today\'s homes, offering a comprehensive range of smart solutions designed to enhance your comfort, convenience, and security. Our state-of-the-art products seamlessly integrate into your lifestyle, allowing you to control and monitor your home environment from anywhere in the world. Discover the power of true automation and peace of mind with our cutting-edge offerings:</p>		\r\n													<img width=\"170\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Group-1-copy.png\" alt=\"\" />													\r\n													<img width=\"64\" height=\"62\" src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shape-1.png\" alt=\"\" />													\r\n				<h2>Smart Home  Automation Solutions</h2>\r\n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 352 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M176 80c-52.94 0-96 43.06-96 96 0 8.84 7.16 16 16 16s16-7.16 16-16c0-35.3 28.72-64 64-64 8.84 0 16-7.16 16-16s-7.16-16-16-16zM96.06 459.17c0 3.15.93 6.22 2.68 8.84l24.51 36.84c2.97 4.46 7.97 7.14 13.32 7.14h78.85c5.36 0 10.36-2.68 13.32-7.14l24.51-36.84c1.74-2.62 2.67-5.7 2.68-8.84l.05-43.18H96.02l.04 43.18zM176 0C73.72 0 0 82.97 0 176c0 44.37 16.45 84.85 43.56 115.78 16.64 18.99 42.74 58.8 52.42 92.16v.06h48v-.12c-.01-4.77-.72-9.51-2.15-14.07-5.59-17.81-22.82-64.77-62.17-109.67-20.54-23.43-31.52-53.15-31.61-84.14-.2-73.64 59.67-128 127.95-128 70.58 0 128 57.42 128 128 0 30.97-11.24 60.85-31.65 84.14-39.11 44.61-56.42 91.47-62.1 109.46a47.507 47.507 0 0 0-2.22 14.3v.1h48v-.05c9.68-33.37 35.78-73.18 52.42-92.16C335.55 260.85 352 220.37 352 176 35