                        \r\n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M634.91 154.88C457.74-8.99 182.19-8.93 5.09 154.88c-6.66 6.16-6.79 16.59-.35 22.98l34.24 33.97c6.14 6.1 16.02 6.23 22.4.38 145.92-133.68 371.3-133.71 517.25 0 6.38 5.85 16.26 5.71 22.4-.38l34.24-33.97c6.43-6.39 6.3-16.82-.36-22.98zM320 352c-35.35 0-64 28.65-64 64s28.65 64 64 64 64-28.65 64-64-28.65-64-64-64zm202.67-83.59c-115.26-101.93-290.21-101.82-405.34 0-6.9 6.1-7.12 16.69-.57 23.15l34.44 33.99c6 5.92 15.66 6.32 22.05.8 83.95-72.57 209.74-72.41 293.49 0 6.39 5.52 16.05 5.13 22.05-.8l34.44-33.99c6.56-6.46 6.33-17.06-.56-23.15z\"></path></svg>                \r\n                            <h4>Wi-Fi Mesh Network</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p>Reliable Wi-Fi Mesh network for extensive coverage. Ensures continuous operation even during internet downtimes.</p>                                                                            \r\n													<img width=\"180\" height=\"170\" src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Group-1-copy-4.png\" alt=\"\" />													\r\n			<h2>Why Choose Smart of Things?\r\n</h2>		\r\n		<p><strong>Embrace the Future with Smart of Things:</strong> Join us in transforming living spaces into intelligent, secure, and comfortable homes. With Smart of Things, you\'re not just making a smart choice; you\'re making a choice for a smarter lifestyle. Discover the difference innovation, quality, and dedication can make in your home today.</p>		\r\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                            <h4>Unmatched Expertise in Innovation</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p>At Smart of Things, our commitment to innovation is not just a slogan—it\'s the cornerstone of our identity. Established in 2023, our team is composed of visionary engineers and developers dedicated to advancing the field of smart home automation. With a relentless focus on research and development, we ensure that every product we offer is at the forefront of technology, providing solutions that are not only effective but revolutionary.</p>                                                                            \r\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                            <h4>Tailored Solutions for Every Home</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p>We understand that every home is unique, which is why we offer flexible and customized services. Whether it\'s tweaking hardware functionalities or personalizing the cloud APP experience, our goal is to ensure that our solutions perfectly align with your lifestyle. Our bespoke services mean that your smart home system is as individual as you are, designed to meet your specific needs and preferences.</p>                                                                            \r\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                            <h4>Quality That You Can Trust</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p>Our products undergo rigorous testing to ensure they meet the highest standards of quality and reliability. With certifications like CE and RoHS, you can be confident that you\'re choosing solutions that have been recognized for their excellence and safety. Additionally, we back our confidence in our products with a 3-year warranty, offering you peace of mind and a guarantee of our commitment to quality.</p>                                                                            \r\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                            <h4>Accessibility and Affordability</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p>We believe that smart home technology should be accessible to everyone. That\'s why we are dedicated to providing affordable smart home and security products without compromising on quality or functionality. Our competitive pricing, combined with customizable packages and flexible financing options, means that transforming your home into a smart home is more achievable than ever.</p>                                                                            \r\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                            <h4>Comprehensive Support and Service</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p>When you choose Smart of Things, you\'re not just buying a product—you\'re gaining a partner in smart home technology. Our professional sales and engineering teams are here to support you every step of the way, from initial consultation to post-installation support. We pride ourselves on our high-efficiency customer service, ensuring that any queries or issues are resolved promptly and satisfactorily.</p>                                                                            \r\n			<h1>Our Projects</h1>		\r\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2150885583-1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                            <h4>Smart Security and Surveillance Installation</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p><ul><li><strong>Overview:</strong> A comprehensive smart security system implementation for a residential complex, integrating intelligent CCTV cameras, motion sensors, and door/window sensors, all controlled via a centralized smart panel and mobile app.</li><li><strong>Highlights:</strong> Emphasize the project\'s focus on enhancing safety and peace of mind for residents, showcasing the seamless integration of various security technologies. Include statistics on response time improvement and user satisfaction.</li></ul></p>                                                                            \r\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2150799753-1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                            <h4>Eco-Friendly Smart Home Conversion</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p><ul><li><strong>Overview:</strong> A complete transformation of a traditional home into an eco-friendly smart home, featuring smart lighting, energy-efficient appliances, and an environmental monitoring system that optimizes energy use and reduces carbon footprint.</li><li><strong>Highlights:</strong> Highlight the project\'s contribution to sustainability through intelligent energy management and the homeowner\'s ability to monitor and adjust consumption in real-time for maximum efficiency and environmental impact reduction.</li></ul></p>                                                                            \r\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2150906356.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                            <h4>Smart Office Space Solution</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p><ul><li><strong>Overview:</strong> The transformation of a traditional office space into a smart office, incorporating smart lighting, climate control, conference room booking systems, and an employee access control system, all managed via a smart panel and app.</li><li><strong>Highlights:</strong> Emphasize the project\'s impact on improving workplace efficiency, employee satisfaction, and energy savings. Highlight the integration of smart technology to facilitate seamless operations and the customization options provided for different office needs.</li></ul></p>                                                                            \r\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/Smart%20of%20Things/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-12-at-2.25.19-PM.jpeg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                            <h4>Luxury Smart Home System Integration</h4>\r\n                                                                                                <p><ul><li><strong>Overview:</strong> The installation of a high-end smart home automation system in a luxury property, including voice-controlled smart appliances, automated curtains, and an advanced entertainment system, all integrated into a user-friendly interface.</li><li><strong>Highlights:</strong> Focus on the luxury and convenience aspects, showcasing how the system enhances the homeowner\'s lifestyle through automation and voice control. Detail the custom solutions provided for unique homeowner requests and the integration of cutting-edge technology.</li></ul></p>                                                                            \r\n			<h2>Get in Touch\r\n</h2>		\r\n		<p>Reach out to us for more information or to start making your home smart today!\"</p>		\r\n                            <h6>Location</h6>\r\n                                                                                                <p>Address : Saudi Arabia</p>                                                                            \r\n                            <h6>Email</h6>\r\n                                                                                                <p><a href=\"info: Info@smartthings.sa\" style=\"color: #92a0