d safer, healthier, and smarter through innovative technology. We envision a world where your home seamlessly responds to your needs, offering full control and security no matter where you are.</p>		\n			<h2>Product and Services</h2>		\n		<p><strong>Smart of Things</strong> brings the future of home automation and security into today\'s homes, offering a comprehensive range of smart solutions designed to enhance your comfort, convenience, and security. Our state-of-the-art products seamlessly integrate into your lifestyle, allowing you to control and monitor your home environment from anywhere in the world. Discover the power of true automation and peace of mind with our cutting-edge offerings:</p>		\n													<img width=\"170\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Group-1-copy.png\" alt=\"\" />													\n													<img width=\"64\" height=\"62\" src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shape-1.png\" alt=\"\" />													\n				<h2>Smart Home  Automation Solutions</h2>\n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 352 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M176 80c-52.94 0-96 43.06-96 96 0 8.84 7.16 16 16 16s16-7.16 16-16c0-35.3 28.72-64 64-64 8.84 0 16-7.16 16-16s-7.16-16-16-16zM96.06 459.17c0 3.15.93 6.22 2.68 8.84l24.51 36.84c2.97 4.46 7.97 7.14 13.32 7.14h78.85c5.36 0 10.36-2.68 13.32-7.14l24.51-36.84c1.74-2.62 2.67-5.7 2.68-8.84l.05-43.18H96.02l.04 43.18zM176 0C73.72 0 0 82.97 0 176c0 44.37 16.45 84.85 43.56 115.78 16.64 18.99 42.74 58.8 52.42 92.16v.06h48v-.12c-.01-4.77-.72-9.51-2.15-14.07-5.59-17.81-22.82-64.77-62.17-109.67-20.54-23.43-31.52-53.15-31.61-84.14-.2-73.64 59.67-128 127.95-128 70.58 0 128 57.42 128 128 0 30.97-11.24 60.85-31.65 84.14-39.11 44.61-56.42 91.47-62.1 109.46a47.507 47.507 0 0 0-2.22 14.3v.1h48v-.05c9.68-33.37 35.78-73.18 52.42-92.16C335.55 260.85 352 220.37 352 176 352 78.8 273.2 0 176 0z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Smart Lighting</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Transform your home\'s ambiance with adjustable brightness and colors. Control lighting scenes remotely for every occasion.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M466.5 83.7l-192-80a48.15 48.15 0 0 0-36.9 0l-192 80C27.7 91.1 16 108.6 16 128c0 198.5 114.5 335.7 221.5 380.3 11.8 4.9 25.1 4.9 36.9 0C360.1 472.6 496 349.3 496 128c0-19.4-11.7-36.9-29.5-44.3zM256.1 446.3l-.1-381 175.9 73.3c-3.3 151.4-82.1 261.1-175.8 307.7z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Intelligent Security System</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Secure your home with advanced surveillance and motion sensors. Peace of mind through real-time alerts and monitoring.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 256 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M192 384c0 35.346-28.654 64-64 64s-64-28.654-64-64c0-23.685 12.876-44.349 32-55.417V224c0-17.673 14.327-32 32-32s32 14.327 32 32v104.583c19.124 11.068 32 31.732 32 55.417zm32-84.653c19.912 22.563 32 52.194 32 84.653 0 70.696-57.303 128-128 128-.299 0-.609-.001-.909-.003C56.789 511.509-.357 453.636.002 383.333.166 351.135 12.225 321.755 32 299.347V96c0-53.019 42.981-96 96-96s96 42.981 96 96v203.347zM208 384c0-34.339-19.37-52.19-32-66.502V96c0-26.467-21.533-48-48-48S80 69.533 80 96v221.498c-12.732 14.428-31.825 32.1-31.999 66.08-.224 43.876 35.563 80.116 79.423 80.42L128 464c44.112 0 80-35.888 80-80z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Environmental Monitoring</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Optimize your living environment with smart sensors. Automatic adjustments for temperature, air quality, and humidity.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M320,32a32,32,0,0,0-64,0v96h64Zm48,128H16A16,16,0,0,0,0,176v32a16,16,0,0,0,16,16H32v32A160.07,160.07,0,0,0,160,412.8V512h64V412.8A160.07,160.07,0,0,0,352,256V224h16a16,16,0,0,0,16-16V176A16,16,0,0,0,368,160ZM128,32a32,32,0,0,0-64,0v96h64Z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Smart Appliance Control</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Simplify daily tasks with remote appliance management. Preheat ovens, schedule coffee makers, and more with ease.</p>                                                                            \n				<h2>Features &amp;  Benefits</h2>\n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M272 0H48C21.5 0 0 21.5 0 48v416c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h224c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V48c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zM160 480c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32 32 14.3 32 32-14.3 32-32 32zm112-108c0 6.6-5.4 12-12 12H60c-6.6 0-12-5.4-12-12V60c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12h200c6.6 0 12 5.4 12 12v312z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Full Remote Access</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Our intuitive app offers complete control of your home from anywhere, ensuring convenience and ease of use.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 352 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M176 352c53.02 0 96-42.98 96-96V96c0-53.02-42.98-96-96-96S80 42.98 80 96v160c