d safer, healthier, and smarter through innovative technology. We envision a world where your home seamlessly responds to your needs, offering full control and security no matter where you are.</p>		\n			<h2>Product and Services</h2>		\n		<p><strong>Smart of Things</strong> brings the future of home automation and security into today\'s homes, offering a comprehensive range of smart solutions designed to enhance your comfort, convenience, and security. Our state-of-the-art products seamlessly integrate into your lifestyle, allowing you to control and monitor your home environment from anywhere in the world. Discover the power of true automation and peace of mind with our cutting-edge offerings:</p>		\n													<img width=\"170\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Group-1-copy.png\" alt=\"\" />													\n													<img width=\"64\" height=\"62\" src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shape-1.png\" alt=\"\" />													\n				<h2>Smart Home  Automation Solutions</h2>\n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 352 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M176 80c-52.94 0-96 43.06-96 96 0 8.84 7.16 16 16 16s16-7.16 16-16c0-35.3 28.72-64 64-64 8.84 0 16-7.16 16-16s-7.16-16-16-16zM96.06 459.17c0 3.15.93 6.22 2.68 8.84l24.51 36.84c2.97 4.46 7.97 7.14 13.32 7.14h78.85c5.36 0 10.36-2.68 13.32-7.14l24.51-36.84c1.74-2.62 2.67-5.7 2.68-8.84l.05-43.18H96.02l.04 43.18zM176 0C73.72 0 0 82.97 0 176c0 44.37 16.45 84.85 43.56 115.78 16.64 18.99 42.74 58.8 52.42 92.16v.06h48v-.12c-.01-4.77-.72-9.51-2.15-14.07-5.59-17.81-22.82-64.77-62.17-109.67-20.54-23.43-31.52-53.15-31.61-84.14-.2-73.64 59.67-128 127.95-128 70.58 0 128 57.42 128 128 0 30.97-11.24 60.85-31.65 84.14-39.11 44.61-56.42 91.47-62.1 109.46a47.507 47.507 0 0 0-2.22 14.3v.1h48v-.05c9.68-33.37 35.78-73.18 52.42-92.16C335.55 260.85 352 220.37 352 176 352 78.8 273.2 0 176 0z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Smart Lighting</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Transform your home\'s ambiance with adjustable brightness and colors. Control lighting scenes remotely for every occasion.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M466.5 83.7l-192-80a48.15 48.15 0 0 0-36.9 0l-192 80C27.7 91.1 16 108.6 16 128c0 198.5 114.5 335.7 221.5 380.3 11.8 4.9 25.1 4.9 36.9 0C360.1 472.6 496 349.3 496 128c0-19.4-11.7-36.9-29.5-44.3zM256.1 446.3l-.1-381 175.9 73.3c-3.3 151.4-82.1 261.1-175.8 307.7z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Intelligent Security System</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Secure your home with advanced surveillance and motion sensors. Peace of mind through real-time alerts and monitoring.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 256 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M192 384c0 35.346-28.654 64-64 64s-64-28.654-64-64c0-23.685 12.876-44.349 32-55.417V224c0-17.673 14.327-32 32-32s32 14.327 32 32v104.583c19.124 11.068 32 31.732 32 55.417zm32-84.653c19.912 22.563 32 52.194 32 84.653 0 70.696-57.303 128-128 128-.299 0-.609-.001-.909-.003C56.789 511.509-.357 453.636.002 383.333.166 351.135 12.225 321.755 32 299.347V96c0-53.019 42.981-96 96-96s96 42.981 96 96v203.347zM208 384c0-34.339-19.37-52.19-32-66.502V96c0-26.467-21.533-48-48-48S80 69.533 80 96v221.498c-12.732 14.428-31.825 32.1-31.999 66.08-.224 43.876 35.563 80.116 79.423 80.42L128 464c44.112 0 80-35.888 80-80z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Environmental Monitoring</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Optimize your living environment with smart sensors. Automatic adjustments for temperature, air quality, and humidity.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M320,32a32,32,0,0,0-64,0v96h64Zm48,128H16A16,16,0,0,0,0,176v32a16,16,0,0,0,16,16H32v32A160.07,160.07,0,0,0,160,412.8V512h64V412.8A160.07,160.07,0,0,0,352,256V224h16a16,16,0,0,0,16-16V176A16,16,0,0,0,368,160ZM128,32a32,32,0,0,0-64,0v96h64Z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Smart Appliance Control</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Simplify daily tasks with remote appliance management. Preheat ovens, schedule coffee makers, and more with ease.</p>                                                                            \n				<h2>Features &amp;  Benefits</h2>\n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M272 0H48C21.5 0 0 21.5 0 48v416c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h224c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V48c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zM160 480c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32 32 14.3 32 32-14.3 32-32 32zm112-108c0 6.6-5.4 12-12 12H60c-6.6 0-12-5.4-12-12V60c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12h200c6.6 0 12 5.4 12 12v312z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Full Remote Access</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Our intuitive app offers complete control of your home from anywhere, ensuring convenience and ease of use.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 352 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M176 352c53.02 0 96-42.98 96-96V96c0-53.02-42.98-96-96-96S80 42.98 80 96v160c0 53.02 42.98 96 96 96zm160-160h-16c-8.84 0-16 7.16-16 16v48c0 74.8-64.49 134.82-140.79 127.38C96.71 376.89 48 317.11 48 250.3V208c0-8.84-7.16-16-16-16H16c-8.84 0-16 7.16-16 16v40.16c0 89.64 63.97 169.55 152 181.69V464H96c-8.84 0-16 7.16-16 16v16c0 8.84 7.16 16 16 16h160c8.84 0 16-7.16 16-16v-16c0-8.84-7.16-16-16-16h-56v-33.77C285.71 418.47 352 344.9 352 256v-48c0-8.84-7.16-16-16-16z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Alexa Voice Control</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Seamless Alexa integration for voice commands. Control your smart home effortlessly, making daily routines simpler.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 576 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M519.442 288.651c-41.519 0-59.5 31.593-82.058 31.593C377.409 320.244 432 144 432 144s-196.288 80-196.288-3.297c0-35.827 36.288-46.25 36.288-85.985C272 19.216 243.885 0 210.539 0c-34.654 0-66.366 18.891-66.366 56.346 0 41.364 31.711 59.277 31.711 81.75C175.885 207.719 0 166.758 0 166.758v333.237s178.635 41.047 178.635-28.662c0-22.473-40-40.107-40-81.471 0-37.456 29.25-56.346 63.577-56.346 33.673 0 61.788 19.216 61.788 54.717 0 39.735-36.288 50.158-36.288 85.985 0 60.803 129.675 25.73 181.23 25.73 0 0-34.725-120.101 25.827-120.101 35.962 0 46.423 36.152 86.308 36.152C556.712 416 576 387.99 576 354.443c0-34.199-18.962-65.792-56.558-65.792z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Compatibility &amp; Integration</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Supports over 100+ devices, creating a unified and connected smart home ecosystem for enhanced functionality.</p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M634.91 154.88C457.74-8.99 182.19-8.93 5.09 154.88c-6.66 6.16-6.79 16.59-.35 22.98l34.24 33.97c6.14 6.1 16.02 6.23 22.4.38 145.92-133.68 371.3-133.71 517.25 0 6.38 5.85 16.26 5.71 22.4-.38l34.24-33.97c6.43-6.39 6.3-16.82-.36-22.98zM320 352c-35.35 0-64 28.65-64 64s28.65 64 64 64 64-28.65 64-64-28.65-64-64-64zm202.67-83.59c-115.26-101.93-290.21-101.82-405.34 0-6.9 6.1-7.12 16.69-.57 23.15l34.44 33.99c6 5.92 15.66 6.32 22.05.8 83.95-72.57 209.74-72.41 293.49 0 6.39 5.52 16.05 5.13 22.05-.8l34.44-33.99c6.56-6.46 6.33-17.06-.56-23.15z\"></path></svg>                \n                            <h4>Wi-Fi Mesh Network</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Reliable Wi-Fi Mesh network for extensive coverage. Ensures continuous operation even during internet downtimes.</p>                                                                            \n													<img width=\"180\" height=\"170\" src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Group-1-copy-4.png\" alt=\"\" />													\n			<h2>Why Choose Smart of Things?\n</h2>		\n		<p><strong>Embrace the Future with Smart of Things:</strong> Join us in transforming living spaces into intelligent, secure, and comfortable homes. With Smart of Things, you\'re not just making a smart choice; you\'re making a choice for a smarter lifestyle. Discover the difference innovation, quality, and dedication can make in your home today.</p>		\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            <h4>Unmatched Expertise in Innovation</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>At Smart of Things, our commitment to innovation is not just a slogan—it\'s the cornerstone of our identity. Established in 2023, our team is composed of visionary engineers and developers dedicated to advancing the field of smart home automation. With a relentless focus on research and development, we ensure that every product we offer is at the forefront of technology, providing solutions that are not only effective but revolutionary.</p>                                                                            \n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            <h4>Tailored Solutions for Every Home</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>We understand that every home is unique, which is why we offer flexible and customized services. Whether it\'s tweaking hardware functionalities or personalizing the cloud APP experience, our goal is to ensure that our solutions perfectly align with your lifestyle. Our bespoke services mean that your smart home system is as individual as you are, designed to meet your specific needs and preferences.</p>                                                                            \n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            <h4>Quality That You Can Trust</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>Our products undergo rigorous testing to ensure they meet the highest standards of quality and reliability. With certifications like CE and RoHS, you can be confident that you\'re choosing solutions that have been recognized for their excellence and safety. Additionally, we back our confidence in our products with a 3-year warranty, offering you peace of mind and a guarantee of our commitment to quality.</p>                                                                            \n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            <h4>Accessibility and Affordability</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>We believe that smart home technology should be accessible to everyone. That\'s why we are dedicated to providing affordable smart home and security products without compromising on quality or functionality. Our competitive pricing, combined with customizable packages and flexible financing options, means that transforming your home into a smart home is more achievable than ever.</p>                                                                            \n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            <h4>Comprehensive Support and Service</h4>\n                                                                                                <p>When you choose Smart of Things, you\'re not just buying a product—you\'re gaining a partner in smart home technology. Our professional sales and engineering teams are here to support you every step of the way, from initial consultation to post-installation support. We pride ourselves on our high-efficiency customer service, ensuring that any queries or issues are resolved promptly and satisfactorily.</p>                                                                            \n			<h1>Our Projects</h1>		\n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2150885583-1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            <h4>Smart Security and Surveillance Installation</h4>\n                                                                                                <p><ul><li><strong>Overview:</strong> A comprehensive smart security system implementation for a residential complex, integrating intelligent CCTV cameras, motion sensors, and door/window sensors, all controlled via a centralized smart panel and mobile app.</li><li><strong>Highlights:</strong> Emphasize the project\'s focus on enhancing safety and peace of mind for residents, showcasing the seamless integration of various security technologies. Include statistics on response time improvement and user satisfaction.</li></ul></p>                                                                            \n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2150799753-1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            <h4>Eco-Friendly Smart Home Conversion</h4>\n                                                                                                <p><ul><li><strong>Overview:</strong> A complete transformation of a traditional home into an eco-friendly smart home, featuring smart lighting, energy-efficient appliances, and an environmental monitoring system that optimizes energy use and reduces carbon footprint.</li><li><strong>Highlights:</strong> Highlight the project\'s contribution to sustainability through intelligent energy management and the homeowner\'s ability to monitor and adjust consumption in real-time for maximum efficiency and environmental impact reduction.</li></ul></p>                                                                            \n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2150906356.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            <h4>Smart Office Space Solution</h4>\n                                                                                                <p><ul><li><strong>Overview:</strong> The transformation of a traditional office space into a smart office, incorporating smart lighting, climate control, conference room booking systems, and an employee access control system, all managed via a smart panel and app.</li><li><strong>Highlights:</strong> Emphasize the project\'s impact on improving workplace efficiency, employee satisfaction, and energy savings. Highlight the integration of smart technology to facilitate seamless operations and the customization options provided for different office needs.</li></ul></p>                                                                            \n                            <img src=\"http://localhost/SmartHomeSolutions/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-12-at-2.25.19-PM.jpeg\" alt=\"\">\n                            <h4>Luxury Smart Home System Integration</h4>\n                                                                                                <p><ul><li><strong>Overview:</strong> The installation of a high-end smart home automation system in a luxury property, including voice-controlled smart appliances, automated curtains, and an advanced entertainment system, all integrated into a user-friendly interface.</li><li><strong>Highlights:</strong> Focus on the luxury and convenience aspects, showcasing how the system enhances the homeowner\'s lifestyle through automation and voice control. Detail the custom solutions provided for unique homeowner requests and the integration of cutting-edge technology.</li></ul></p>                                                                            \n			<h2>Get in Touch\n</h2>		\n		<p>Reach out to us for more information or to start making your home smart today!\"</p>		\n                            <h6>Location</h6>\n                                                                                                <p>Address : Saudi Arabia</p>                                                                            \n                            <h6>Email</h6>\n                                                                                                <p><a href=\"info: Info@smartthings.sa\" style=\"color: #92a0a6\"> Info@smartthings.sa</a></p>                                                                            \n                    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"ht